# Monorepo conventions

- Keep service boundaries explicit: `datalake`, `mcp-stocklake`, `api-gateway`, `analytics`, `screener`.
- Treat `datalake` as system of record and avoid duplicating canonical state across services.
- Keep scaffold changes lightweight: no business logic unless explicitly requested.
- Require docs and tests to evolve together with each service implementation.
